Student Car Share is an  innovative start-up whose technology enables students 18+ with a G2 license to rent cars 24/7 with self serve access starting at $6 an hour.  Reservations include gas and insurance. They launched in Waterloo with cars parked on campus at St. Paul's University College, off campus at 315 King Street North and 328 Regina Street North.

